{"id":1751,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":468,"title":"Conversation 238","subtitle":"Café Flyer Reorder Request","level":"B1","parts":15,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-238.1751/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/0-conversation-238.mp3","transcript":"Hey, I need to reorder some flyers for my café's grand reopening next month.\nCan you help me with that?\nSure, I can.\nLet me check...\noh, you're with The Cozy Corner, right?\nDidn't I design some flyers for you last year?\nYep, that's right.\nBut we've updated our logo and added a new menu,\nso I'll need the design to reflect that.\nGot it.\nI can have those updated and printed by the end of the week.\nBy the way, would you like to see some paper options?\nMaybe something sturdier than last time?\nOh, that's a great idea.\nLet's go for it.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:03:59","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hey, I need to reorder some flyers for my café's grand reopening next month.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/1.mp3","time_start":0.0,"time_end":4.47},{"position":2,"content":"Can you help me with that?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/2.mp3","time_start":4.68,"time_end":5.93},{"position":3,"content":"Sure, I can.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/3.mp3","time_start":6.2,"time_end":7.67},{"position":4,"content":"Let me check...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/4.mp3","time_start":7.67,"time_end":9.01},{"position":5,"content":"oh, you're with The Cozy Corner, right?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/5.mp3","time_start":9.21,"time_end":11.2},{"position":6,"content":"Didn't I design some flyers for you last year?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/6.mp3","time_start":11.2,"time_end":13.8},{"position":7,"content":"Yep, that's right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/7.mp3","time_start":14.04,"time_end":15.24},{"position":8,"content":"But we've updated our logo and added a new menu,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/8.mp3","time_start":15.24,"time_end":18.05},{"position":9,"content":"so I'll need the design to reflect that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/9.mp3","time_start":18.05,"time_end":20.12},{"position":10,"content":"Got it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/10.mp3","time_start":20.12,"time_end":20.9},{"position":11,"content":"I can have those updated and printed by the end of the week.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/11.mp3","time_start":20.9,"time_end":24.13},{"position":12,"content":"By the way, would you like to see some paper options?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/12.mp3","time_start":24.13,"time_end":27.22},{"position":13,"content":"Maybe something sturdier than last time?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/13.mp3","time_start":27.22,"time_end":29.82},{"position":14,"content":"Oh, that's a great idea.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/14.mp3","time_start":29.82,"time_end":31.4},{"position":15,"content":"Let's go for it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-238-2024-10-25-13-57-04/15.mp3","time_start":31.4,"time_end":32.48}]}